==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Expansible
<hw>Ex*pan"si*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>expansible</ets>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being expanded or spread
out widely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Bodies are not <qex>expansible</qex> in proportion to their
weight.</q> <rj><qau>Grew.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Ex*pan"si*ble*ness</wf> ,<pos>n.</pos>
-<wf>Ex*pan"si*bly</wf> ,<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expansile</ent>⟦br⟧
